Inc.;
(c) A psychologist with the health service provider designation, a psychological practitioner, a certified
psychologist, or a psychological associate licensed under the provisions of KRS Chapter 319;
(d) A licensed registered nurse with:
1. A master's degree in psychiatric nursing from an accredited institution and two (2) years of
clinical experience with mentally ill persons;[,] or[ a licensed registered nurse with]

