designated worker for the purpose of making preliminary inquiries;
(57)[(56)] "Risk and needs assessment" means an actuarial tool scientifically proven to identify specific factors
and needs that are related to delinquent and noncriminal misconduct;
(58)[(57)] "Safety plan" means a written agreement developed by the cabinet and agreed to by a family that clearly
